This paper discusses issues of fairness in machine learning, specifically in the context of recommendation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also discusses information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CR) in the context of fairness in recommendation systems. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of fairness on societal issues (cs.SI) such as discrimination and bias. Finally, the paper mentions the use of recommender systems in the context of e-commerce (cs.CY).
